{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"0162c28767","title":"斗争要文明些，坚持文斗，不用武斗","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"eb4796153a","index":0,"year":1967,"month":2,"day":3,"articleId":"0162c28767"}],"tags":[{"id":"40ffd466ef","name":"武斗","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji49","name":"毛泽东全集第49卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/49-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji49":{"comments":[{"id":"b779813aa2","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"0162c28767","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是毛泽东关于斗争问题给周恩来的一段指示。"}],"contents":[{"id":"cf2375336b","type":"title","text":"斗争要文明些，坚持文斗，不用武斗”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"0162c28767"},{"id":"b779813aa2","type":"paragraph","text":"斗争要文明些，我们是无产阶级专政，要高姿态，要高风格北京街头上标语水平不高，到处都是打倒、砸烂狗头，哪有那么多的狗头，都是人头。这样搞群众很难理解。搞喷气式飞机照相片，登报贴在大街上被外国记者搞走了。现在要将斗争水平提高，现在水平太低。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"0162c28767"},{"id":"0016a6c42b","type":"paragraph","text":"八月初，也没这凶嘛，斗倒斗臭要在政治上斗臭，要对后代进行教育。不然他们将来掌权了，也这样干，这就太简单化了。他们认为这样斗臭了，还有把别人生活上的问题摆出来也叫斗臭了，我看不合适。主要是政治上斗臭","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"0162c28767"}],"page":{"id":"a1766bb50f","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"0162c28767","start":304,"end":304}}}},"__N_SSG":true}